      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «صَوْمُ شَهْرِ شَعْبَانَ وَ شَهْرِ رَمَضَانَ شَهْرَيْنِ مُتَتَابِعَيْنِ تَوْبَةٌ وَ اَللَّهِ مِنَ اَللَّهِ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1825 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Fasting the Month of Sha‘ban and Month of Ramadan consecutively is repentance, by Allah (swt), from Allah (swt).\""
        ]
      }
